MELILLA

01:53:40.417 --> 01:53:46.667
{\an8}IN 2018, MORE THAN 70 MILLION PEOPLE
LEFT THEIR HOMES

01:53:46.792 --> 01:53:50.958
{\an8}SEARCHING FOR A BETTER WORLD.

